      <h1>Pakistani Nikah Nama Translation</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Column-by-Column Guide for UAE</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">The Pakistani Nikah Nama is one of the most complex documents we translate. With 20+ columns in Urdu, handwritten entries, and Islamic legal terminology, it requires specialized expertise. This guide explains every step from Pakistan to UAE acceptance.</p>

      <div class="service-snapshot">
        <div class="snapshot-item">
          <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
          <span><strong>Document:</strong> Nikah Nama (نکاح نامہ)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="snapshot-item">
